    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Comparison of the heads of (A) the holotype of Blythia hmuifang sp. nov. (MZMU 714), (B) a paratype of Blythia hmuifang sp. nov. (MZMU 716) and (C) B. reticulata (MZU 802)." ;
