<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.808084>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Map showing the distribution of Blythia hmuifang sp. nov. and the known distribution of B. reticulata: 1. Htingnam; 2. Sumprabum; 3. Gandhigram; 4. Renging, Janakmukh and Rotung; 5. Dejoo, of North Lakhimpur; 6. Dafla Hill; 7. Itanagar; 8. Chessa; 9. Orang National Park; 10. Upper Shillong; 11. Shillong; 12. Cherrapunji; 13. Samagooting; 14. Kohima; 15. Ukhrul; 16. Lawachara Reserve; 17. Sawleng; 18. Sihphir; 19. Sihhmui; 20. Durtlang and Aizawl; 21. Hmuifang; 22. Lungkawlh; 23. Fort White; 24. Hakka." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/808084/files/figure.png" ;
